  <data key="d2">The Starbucks Elegant Pink Purple Romantic Mug is a distinctive product offered for sale at a price of 90.06 yuan. This mug is characterized by its elegant design and unique color scheme, which includes shades of pink and purple. It is specifically associated with the Starbucks brand, reflecting the company's commitment to stylish and appealing merchandise.

